Subject: effect on protein 3D structure [VariO:0064]
Value: Variation affecting protein three dimensional structure.

Subject: effect on protein tertiary structure [VariO:0070]
Value: Variation affecting protein three dimensional structure.

Subject: nonsynonymous variation [VariO:0017]
Value: mRNA variation leading to amino acid change in translated protein. The variant alters the codon so that it encodes another amino acid.

Subject: synonymous variation [VariO:0343]
Value: mRNA variation not affecting the sequence of the translated protein.
